# Reports directory
This directory will contain generated validation reports in various formats.

## Report Types
- HTML reports: Comprehensive visual reports with interactive elements
- JSON reports: Machine-readable data for integration and analysis
- Markdown reports: Documentation-friendly format for sharing
- CSV reports: Spreadsheet-compatible data for analysis

## File Naming Convention
- Format: `validation-report-{timestamp}-{format}.{ext}`
- Example: `validation-report-2024-01-15T10-30-00-html.html`

## Retention
Reports should be archived or cleaned up periodically to manage disk space.
Consider keeping the most recent reports and archiving older ones.